  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  Would be there any difference in dopamine synthesis between remitted clinical high risk
           subjects for psychosis and healthy control?

        -  What would happen to dopamine synthesis after antipsychotic discontinuation in clinical
           high risk subjects for psychosis?

        -  What about the dopamine synthesis in recurred clinical high risk subjects for psychosis
           after the discontinuation?
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      After the antipsychotic medication discontinuation, we are going to assess the changes of the
      biological markers
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
